[22570]={"割碎","35能量 近战范围\n瞬发 10秒 冷却\n需要 猎豹形态\n[q]终结技，对目标造成伤害并使其瘫痪。任何直接伤害都会使目标醒来。根据连击点数的数量决定伤害和瘫痪效果的持续时间：\n 1点：(84 + 45 + [Mainhand weapon min damage])-(84 + 45 + [Mainhand weapon max damage])伤害，2秒\n 2点：(84 * 2 + 45 + [Mainhand weapon min damage])-(84 * 2 + 45 + [Mainhand weapon max damage])伤害，3秒\n 3点：(84 * 3 + 45 + [Mainhand weapon min damage])-(84 * 3 + 45 + [Mainhand weapon max damage])伤害，4秒\n 4点：(84 * 4 + 45 + [Mainhand weapon min damage])-(84 * 4 + 45 + [Mainhand weapon max damage])伤害，5秒\n 5点：(84 * 5 + 45 + [Mainhand weapon min damage])-(84 * 5 + 45 + [Mainhand weapon max damage])伤害，6秒"},
